Package rs.kreme.ksbot.api.queries

Class Query<T,​Q extends Query<T,​Q>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • rs.kreme.ksbot.api.queries.Query<T,​Q>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the objects in the query.
    Q - the type of the query class extending this base class.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EquipmentItemQuery, GraphicsObjectQuery, ItemQuery, NPCQuery, PlayerQuery, TileItemQuery, TileObjectQuery, TradePostQuery, WidgetQuery
    public abstract class Query<T,​Q extends Query<T,​Q>>
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic utility class for querying and filtering collections of objects with a fluent API design.
